modShortDescription: This mod increases the size of the player backpack to 120.
modDescription:
This mod increases the size of the player [backpack](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-backpack/) to 120.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/Donovan522/donovan-7d2d-modlets/tree/stable/donovan-megabackpack)**

If you find any issues or have a suggestion for improvement, please [open an issue](https://github.com/Donovan522/donovan-7d2d-modlets/issues) and Donovan will look into it ASAP.
